Place the apple on the side table.

Place the apple on the side table

high_descs: Turn left, turn right, move forward and turn right to the dining table.
Take an apple from the dining table.
Turn left and turn right to the microwave.
Place an apple in the microwave, wait for a while, and then take it out.

Place an apple in the side table.
